parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the 6.0L engine can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially in emergency response situations like ambulance services.
The failure of the EGR cooler can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine failure, stalling, or loss of power, which can result in accidents or injuries.
The starting and running problems can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially in emergency response situations like ambulance services.
